<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Gestofol Incentive Calculator</h1>
        <label for="salesCategory">Select Sales Category:</label>
        <select id="salesCategory">
            <option value="A">Category A (Below 2 Lakh Sales)</option>
            <option value="B">Category B (2 Lakh and Above Sales)</option>
        </select>
        <br>
        <label for="salesQuantity">Enter Sales Quantity (in strips):</label>
        <input type="number" id="salesQuantity" min="1" placeholder="Enter quantity">
        <button onclick="calculateIncentive()">Calculate Incentive</button>
        <p id="result"></p>
    </div>
    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," id="moneyImage" alt="Money Image" style="display: none; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); z-index: 9999; animation: moneyShower 1s ease-in-out forwards;">
    
    <script>
        function calculateIncentive() {
            const salesCategory = document.getElementById('salesCategory').value;
            const salesQuantity = parseInt(document.getElementById('salesQuantity').value);
            let incentivePerStrip = 0;

            if (salesCategory === 'A') {
                if (salesQuantity >= 1 && salesQuantity <= 300) {
                    incentivePerStrip = 3;
                } else if (salesQuantity >= 301 && salesQuantity <= 500) {
                    incentivePerStrip = 4;
                } else if (salesQuantity > 500) {
                    incentivePerStrip = 8;
                } else {
                    alert('Please enter a valid sales quantity.');
                    return;
                }
            } else if (salesCategory === 'B') {
                if (salesQuantity >= 1 && salesQuantity <= 300) {
                    incentivePerStrip = 5;
                } else if (salesQuantity >= 301 && salesQuantity <= 500) {
                    incentivePerStrip = 8;
                } else if (salesQuantity > 500) {
                    incentivePerStrip = 15;
                } else {
                    alert('Please enter a valid sales quantity.');
                    return;
                }
            }

            const totalIncentive = salesQuantity * incentivePerStrip;
            const resultElement = document.getElementById('result');
            resultElement.innerHTML = `Total Incentive: Rs ${totalIncentive}`;
            resultElement.style.display = 'block';

            const moneyImage = document.getElementById('moneyImage');
            moneyImage.style.display = 'block';
            setTimeout(() => {
                moneyImage.style.display = 'none';
            }, 1000); // Hide the image after 1 second (same duration as animation)
        }
    </script>
</body>
